headline: Investors Eye AI Winners on Both Sides of Pacific: Ives
summary: Dan Ives, Wedbush Securities Managing Director and Global Head of Tech Research, says cybersecurity is on the outside looking in but will be "very strong in the AI revolution." He tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on "The Close" that ripple-effect names like CrowdStrike and Palo Alto are well positioned.
